articles.author: Jordan Mendoza
articles.title: American teenager Learner Tien stuns No. 5 Daniil Medvedev in Australian Open - USA TODAY
articles.description: At the age of 19, Learner Tien defeated Daniil Medvedev in a five-set thriller that finished just before 3 a.m. in Melbourne.
articles.content:
There's been a stunner at the Australian Open, and it came from an American teenager.
Qualifier and 19-year-old Learner Tien beat No. 5-ranked and three-time Australian Open finalist Daniil Medvedev… [+1557 chars]
